Base settings:

  --------------------------------------------------------
  setting              default
  --------------------------------------------------------
  fgcolor              user
  bgcolor              user
  font                 user
  tab-frame-image      /$/tabframe
  gbutton-frame-image  /$/gbutton
  --------------------------------------------------------


